## Task 2 Environment and Setup

Objective: Prepare the lab environment.
- AttackBox: preinstalled with Gobuster.
- -Lab Machine: Ubuntu 20.04 VM hosting multiple subdomains, vhosts, and CMS (WordPress, Joomla).
- DNS setup: edit /etc/resolv-dnsmasq to include nameserver MACHINE_IP.
